    </div>
    <p class="col-vision">We're building a community server to keep things competitive all year round. It starts with focused weekend tournaments and grows into a full 24/7 server where players create parties, set up their own matches, and compete between clans.</p>
    <div class="col-modes">
      <span class="col-mode">Hunger Games</span>
      <span class="col-mode">Battle Royale</span>
      <span class="col-mode">Prop Hunt</span>
      <span class="col-mode">Survival Games</span>
      <span class="col-mode">Random Item Challenge</span>
      <span class="col-mode">Death Swap</span>
      <span class="col-mode">PvP Tournaments</span>
      <span class="col-mode">Party Matches</span>
      <span class="col-mode">1v1 Duels</span>
      <span class="col-mode">100 Player Events</span>
    </div>

    <button class="col-plan-toggle" id="planToggle" aria-expanded="false">
      Progression Plan
      <svg class="col-plan-chev" viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="13" height="13" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M3 6l5 5 5-5"/></svg>
    </button>
    <div class="col-plan-body" id="planBody">
      <div class="timeline">
        <div class="phase">
          <div class="node">1</div>
          <div class="ptag">WEEKS 1–3</div>
          <h4>Launch</h4>
          <p>Weekend sessions only. Three weeks, three game modes. Hunger Games first, then Battle Royale, then Prop Hunt. Focused and small — we let the community build naturally before scaling up.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="phase">
          <div class="node">2</div>
          <div class="ptag">MONTH 2</div>
          <h4>Expanding</h4>
          <p>Sessions move to 2 to 3 times a week. Survival Games, Random Item Challenge, Death Swap and PvP Tournaments join the schedule. The competitive scene starts to form.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="phase">
          <div class="node">3</div>
          <div class="ptag">POST-EVENT</div>
          <h4>Going 24/7</h4>
          <p>After our 500 player event the server goes fully 24/7. Players create parties, pick from our full game mode selection and host their own matches scaled to their group size. Staff-run official tournaments with prizes every weekend. European PvP clans already in talks to compete in inter-clan tournaments.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

